tech_rep_description: The mineral salts medium contained the following (per liter of demineralized water): 1.55 g of K2HPO4, 0.85 g of NaH2PO4 2H20, 2.0 g of (NH4)2SO4, 0.1 g of MgCl2 6H20, 10 mg of EDTA, 2 mg of ZnSO4 .7H20, 1 mg of CaCl2. 2H20, 5 mg of FeSO4 7H20, 0.2 mg of Na2MoO4. 2H20, 0.2 mg of CuSO4 5H20, 0.4 mg of CoCl2 6H20, and 1 mg of MnCI2 2H20.
